1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
Salom.

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:05,500
Men 1 shaxsiy dasturchi Yeon Sam-heumman.

3
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:08,500
17 yil davomida kompaniyani boshqarib keldim,

4
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:14,000
AI bilan birga 200 dan ortiq veb-sayt,
600,000 sahifa yaratdim.

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Bu mahsulot yangi yaratilmagan.

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,000
8 yil davomida o'sgan vosita — WIA Geulsalim.

7
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Insoniyatning 5 ming yillik bilimining 95%i
hanuzgacha yetib bormagan.

8
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Janubiy Koreya tarixiy hujjatlarning 87%i raqamlashtirilmagan holda
uyquda,

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:40,000
Dunyo bo'ylab 7,000 tilda 97%i,
AI tarjima va ovoz sifatining ancha pastligi yoki umuman yo'qligi bor.

10
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
300 million nogiron shaxslar
hali ham kitobni qo'lga ola olmayapti.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:50,000
Bu to'rt qavatli to'siqni bir marta hal qilish kerak.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,500
Geulsalim 4 bosqichli quvur liniyasi —
tiklash · strukturaviylashtirish · aylantirish · yetkazib berish.

13
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:59,500
Endilikda to'rt ta demo orqali
bevosita ko'rsatamiz.

14
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,000
Birinchi demo — tiklashdir.

15
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:10,000
Diffusion modeli buzilgan tarixiy hujjatlarni tiklaydi,
til modeli yo'qolgan harflarni taxmin qiladi.

16
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Tiklash manipulyatsiya emas.

17
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:20,000
Asli ko'rsatkichlari doimiy saqlanadi.

18
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,000
Ikkinchi demo — strukturaviylashtirishdir.

19
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:36,000
Teglarsiz PDF ni WCAG 2.2 ga muvofiq HTML ga,
AI avtomatik tarzda strukturaviylashtiradi va o'rinli matnlar ishlab chiqaradi.

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:42,000
WIA Book imkoniyatlari tekshirish saytida,
men allaqachon 80 ta bandni avtomatik ravishda tekshiryapman.

21
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
Uchinchi demo — EPUB imkoniyatlarini tiklashdir.

22
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Imkoniyat va standartlarga javob bermaydigan EPUB 2 ni,
EPUB 3 ga avtomatik tiklaydi.

23
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:06,000
80 ta tekshirish bandini to'liq o'tadi.

24
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:13,000
WCAG, EPUB A11y, KS X 6201, Yevropa EAA —
to'rt xalqaro standartlarni bir vaqtda qondiradi.

25
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:19,000
To'rtinchi demo — multimodal yetkazib berishdir.

26
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Braille 7,000 tilda,
ova 254 tilda,

27
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:29,000
WIA Talk 3D qo'l harflari,
436 ta interaktiv vositasi va simulyatori.

28
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:36,000
Dovdirash va ko'rish qobiliyati past shaxslar
tarjimon orqali to'g'ridan-to'g'ri muloqot qilishadi WIA Live,

29
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,500
allaqachon sinovdan o'tmoqda.

30
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,000
Bizning Geulsalim.

31
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:46,000
弘益人間 — umuman foydali qilish, davomiylik bilan.  
We're Geulsalim.
